Third-Party Software Notices
============================

FFmpeg
------

This application includes `ffmpeg.exe`, which is licensed under the GNU General
Public License, version 3 (GPLv3). FFmpeg is copyright © the FFmpeg developers.

Website: https://ffmpeg.org  
License: see LICENSES/ffmpeg-gplv3.txt

The FFmpeg binary is used unmodified and is invoked externally via subprocess.

The FFmpeg source code can be obtained from https://ffmpeg.org/download.html

NeuronBridge API
----------------

This application uses the NeuronBridge API to programmatically access and
download neuron data (e.g., H5J volumes, SWC/OBJ reconstructions).

NeuronBridge is provided by the Janelia Research Campus, HHMI:
https://neuronbridge.janelia.org

All data obtained via the API is owned by Janelia/HHMI and is intended for
non-commercial, scientific, and educational use only. This application is not
affiliated with or endorsed by HHMI or Janelia.

